sequenceDiagram
    actor Student
    participant Web as Flask Web App
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Student->>Web: Open enrolled course
    Web->>DB: Read lessons and progress
    DB-->>Web: Progress records
    Web-->>Student: Display completion percentage
    Student->>Web: Mark lesson completed
    Web->>DB: Update progress.is_completed
    Web->>DB: Update enrollment status when complete
    DB-->>Web: Commit transaction
    Web-->>Student: Display updated percentage

